<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="I" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Insist" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Insist,</orth> to persist in demanding: <cit><quote>yet I --ed,</quote> <bibl n="shak. jc 2.1.245" default="NO" valid="yes">Caes. II, 1, 245</bibl></cit>. With <emph>on</emph>: <cit><quote>--ing on the old prerogative,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cor 3.3.17" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. III, 3, 17</bibl></cit>.
